They must be very surprised.

10
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,164
Candy.

11
00:01:15,442 --> 00:01:18,275
Candy, can you turn off the light?

12
00:01:18,344 --> 00:01:21,142
The time has passed.

13
00:01:21,214 --> 00:01:24,206
Sorry, I'll turn off the light now.

14
00:01:25,018 --> 00:01:28,579
Blanny, you are not going to write a letter home?

15
00:01:28,655 --> 00:01:30,418
To tell them what?

16
00:01:30,490 --> 00:01:34,187
That I am one of the five chosen people,
so please be happy for me?

17
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:38,660
Or should I tell them that
it feels lonely to leave here?

18
00:01:41,067 --> 00:01:44,468
