58
00:04:17,991 --> 00:04:20,687
You are going to the hospital in Chicago
aren't you?

59
00:04:21,361 --> 00:04:22,350
I....

60
00:04:22,428 --> 00:04:26,228
You don't need to hide anything. We've all heard.

61
00:04:26,299 --> 00:04:29,393
You can't hide anything in the hospital.

62
00:04:36,242 --> 00:04:39,700
Sorry,
I didn't mean to hide things from you.

63
